Test Server:
    RAM: min 16G
    HARD: 1T SSD
    CPU: min 4core 3GHz
    OS: Linux Ubuntu or Debian based with SSH access


Production Server:
    ----------------------------------
    Server: database
    RAM: min 16G
    HARD: 2T SSD
    CPU: Multiple 3.2 GHz+ multi-core
    OS: Linux Ubuntu or Debian based with SSH access
    ----------------------------------
    Server: file repository
    RAM: 8G
    HARD: 4T
    CPU: Multiple 3.2 GHz+ multi-core
    OS: Linux Ubuntu or Debian based with SSH access
    ----------------------------------
    Server: backend and frontend
    RAM: 16G
    HARD: 1T
    CPU: Multiple 3.2 GHz+ multi-core
    OS: Linux Ubuntu or Debian based with SSH access

    * database + backend + front end server may be one system configures as a whole or as VMs
    * file server is preferred to be a separated system
